{
  "stem": "1282.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In our village, everybody went to the next town to-- which is not [INAUDIBLE], but so-- because he couldn't go to every small, little community, but in the next biggest.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some were totally, totally against him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to realize that most Jews were very, very religious, to the point-- it's like the extreme Hasidim here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they believed that Jabotinsky spoke ungodly words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why was it ungodly?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he spoke of a land, of Palestine, which God is supposed to give us through the coming of messiah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To be a Zionist was to go against a very traditional concept of, of orthodox Judaism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not popular to be a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were just as many boos as there were people that listened with emotion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was not totally accepted because he was a revisionist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] One word I have trouble to pronounce.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he had new concept, new ideas, and most Jewish people were very old fashioned, traditional, same as their parents were 50 years ago, and 100 years ago.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were people that did not accept him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if the kids organized themselves into a Zionist movement, they were not very popular to kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And sometimes we did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My parents did not object to it, but some kids had to do it without the permission of their parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because, how dare you promote something which is not in the book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's not our time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Messiah will come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's when the time will be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, you're going against God's will.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a fear, ignorance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As, you know, when extremists and fanatics have a way of-- I hate to go on tape and say anything to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It is not my way of doing it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I think you understand what I'm not saying.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
